body:
@iraghumitra looks like the new API isn't being used quite right.

Sample from the dev tools
```
{
  "alerts": [
    {
      "guid": "50a0c1f6-8a55-4cdd-a031-81c53174ad7b",
      "sensorType": [
        "snort",
        "snort"
      ],
      "index": "snort_index_2017.11.20.15"
    },
...
```

This should be, I believe,
```
{
  "alerts": [
    {
      "guid": "50a0c1f6-8a55-4cdd-a031-81c53174ad7b",
      "sensorType": "snort",
      "index": "snort_index_2017.11.20.15"
    },
...
  ],
  "groups": [
    "source:type"
  ]
}
```

Edit: Fixed the original query.  I grabbed something while messing with it a bit.

> Is this the expected output?

I agree with @ottobackwards . That looks like what I would expect to see.  

@JonZeolla I assume since you asked, it is not what you would expect.  What would prefer to see here?
